  <brief_title>Purified Rabies Vaccine for Human Use (Chick-embryo Cell)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluate the Immunogenicity and Safety of Rabies Vaccine Given in a Post-exposure Prophylaxis Regimen to Healthy Children and Adults Aged 10-60 Years.</official_title>
